* ==================== CORE CHANGES ===================

* The option "--vgdb-stop-at=event1,event2,..." accepts the new value abexit.
  This indicates to invoke gdbserver when your program exits abnormally
  (i.e. with a non zero exit code).
* Fix Rust v0 name demangling.
